is transitive plane existed behind [[mirror]]s and other reflective surfaces,<ref group="note">Though this plane was officially named in 3{{rd}} edition, the concept of such a plane originally existed in the 2{{nd}}-edition [[Planescape Campaign Setting|''Planescape'']] module, ''[[Tales from the Infinite Staircase]]''. However, as this plane is referred to in a 3{{rd}}-edition ''Forgotten Realms'' source, this article focuses on such material. such as windows.

In terms of planar traits, the secretive Plane of Mirrors was somewhat similar to the Material Plane. [[Magic]] functioned normal, as did gravity and time. Breathing was normal throughout the plane,{{Cite web/theedverse/2021-12-06 - Mirror Realm}}

There were no naturally-occurring food sources on the plane, though myriad of travelers have brought foreign food within.

